## 🛡️ COMPLIANCE STACK (IRON DOME)

### Insurance (OIC / คปภ.)

**OIC 56/2562 — New Health Standard 2024:**
| Rule | Detail |
|------|--------|
| Coverage Term | "เท่าที่จ่ายจริง" (As Charged) vs "ตามจริง" (Actual) |
| Waiting Period | 30 days (general), 120 days (tumor/cyst/hernia) |
| Guaranteed Renewal | Must state conditions clearly |
| Co-payment Types | Simple Copay vs Deductible vs Co-insurance |

**180-DAY RULE (CRITICAL):**
```
⚠️ If client is REPLACING existing policy:
   → Issue new policy 180 days BEFORE cancelling old policy
   → Reason (Agent): Avoid commission forfeiture
   → Reason (Client): Avoid coverage gap during underwriting
   → MUST MENTION in proposal
```

**Old vs New Standard:**
| Standard | Risk | Action |
|----------|------|--------|
| OLD | Insurer can increase individual premium, refuse renewal | Replace with New Standard |
| NEW (2024) | Individual price increase NOT allowed, cancellation NOT allowed | Keep and renew |

### Investment (SEC / กลต.)

| Rule | Detail |
|------|--------|
| Unit-Linked Disclaimer | "ไม่รับประกันผลตอบแทน" (MANDATORY) |
| Projection Rates | OIC approved: 2%, 5%, 8% ONLY |
| Disclosure | Must disclose fund charges and fee structure |
| **BAN** | NEVER promise specific returns |

### Tax (Revenue Code)

| Type | Limit | Conditions |
|------|-------|------------|
| Life Premium | 100,000 THB | Policy 10+ years |
| Health Premium | 25,000 THB | Combined with life ≤ 100k |
| Annuity | 200,000 THB | With conditions |
| Combined Cap | 500,000 THB | RMF + SSF + PVD + Annuity |

**ANNUITY TRAP (CRITICAL):**
```
⚠️ To receive tax deduction, client MUST:
   1. Hold policy for 5+ years, AND
   2. Reach age 55 before withdrawal
   
   If withdrawn early → Must return ALL tax benefits + penalty
   
   MUST WARN in proposal if recommending annuity.
```

### Privacy (PDPA)

| Rule | Detail |
|------|--------|
| Children's Names | Initials ONLY (ด.ญ. ก., ด.ช. ข.) |
| Client Data | Handle with confidentiality |

