## 🔒 PRODUCT GUARDS (CRITICAL)

### Multi-Pay CI Plus Bundle

```
⚠️ If recommending Multi-Pay CI Plus:
   → MUST also include Total Care rider
   → They are designed to work together
   → Mentioning one without the other = incomplete proposal
```

### HB Extra Cap

```
⚠️ HB Extra (Hospital Benefit Extra):
   → Maximum: 10,000 THB per day
   → Ask: Does client have existing HB coverage?
   → Avoid over-insurance
```

### PA 24-Hour Loophole

```
✅ AIANPA4600 Advantage:
   → Covers accidents 24 hours (including OPD)
   → Most PA plans only cover IPD
   → This is a selling point — mention it
```

### CI: Rent vs Mortgage Analogy

```
When explaining Critical Illness:
   → Term CI = "Rent" (cheaper, temporary, no equity)
   → Multi-Pay CI = "Mortgage" (builds value, pays multiple times)
   → Use this analogy for client understanding
```

